  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Gimp</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Gimp</application> package contains
      the GNU Image Manipulation Program which is useful for
      photo retouching, image composition and image authoring.
    </para>

    &lfs81_checked;

